{"tid":561940,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"89S客量證明左非繁時馬鞍山來往黃泥頭只需要808","createTime":"2018-02-15T12:27:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-15T23:27:34.000Z","uid":108894,"like":6,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"acda4c9e82db464d9680ef061ae7e081f4a7713a","tid":561940,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:27:12.000Z","msg":"班班吉車遊街咁滯，仲陰公過82K<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n證明左根本非繁時808足夠應付<br />\n但係黃泥頭班山頭撚就係都要迫九巴整89S呢條垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n強烈要求89S只於早上番學時間提供服務，用車擺落83X又好，89D又好，非繁唔好再晒油開89S<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，乘客請好好善用808<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n當初屌89D飛黃泥頭班巴打唔該出黎發表下咩事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，好啦嘈到九巴開89S啦你地又唔搭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"707a5935bada896c1f83c713650a5d48db0ed6f7","tid":561940,"uid":29070,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"死巴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"991cb51f9d524c3a579843e46b1068e82305dddd","tid":561940,"uid":108894,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"707a5935bada896c1f83c713650a5d48db0ed6f7","tid":561940,"uid":29070,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T12:38:39.000Z","msg":"死巴膠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-15T13:36:21.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/t/400022/4?ref=android\" target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/t/400022/4?ref=android</a><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/face